<p class="">Would you like to send some troops to help them?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5ce9e2ff-261b-4fe8-91f8-7f19037ad6f4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
