        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-1a6ca8e2-35cb-4238-b494-a65e32d66d7f'>
            
<p class=""><em>It being after Ten of the Clock,</em> Mr. SPEAKER <em>proceeded, pursuant to Standing Order No. 14, to put forthwith the Question necessary to dispose of the Report of the Resolution under consideration.</em></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

